description1.name: Description
description1.value: Welcome to Kerman Avenue, your cozy retreat in the city! This beautifully updated 3-bedroom 2-bathroom has been freshly painted and features new pot lights. Located in a highly desirable Grimsby neighbourhood near the lake, it offers the perfect blend of peace and convenience, with easy access to QEW, Fifty Point Conservation, Winona Crossing and downtown Grimsby. The backyard is a private haven, complete with an ingound pool, a gas BBQ and a sunroom. With lots of living space, including a basement with a separate entrance, this home offers versatility and the potential to create an in-law suite.

summary.name: Summary
value: Beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home on Kerman Avenue.
Freshly painted with new pot lights throughout.
Located in a desirable Grimsby neighborhood near the lake, providing a peaceful yet convenient lifestyle.
Easy access to QEW, Fifty Point Conservation, Winona Crossing, and downtown Grimsby.
Private backyard oasis featuring an inground pool, gas BBQ, and sunroom.
Ample living space, including a basement with a separate entrance for added versatility.
Potential for creating an in-law suite in the basement.
